Create or update a secret in a repository

Usage:
  secrethub save REPO KEY VALUE
  secrethub save (-h|--help)

Options:
  -h --help
    Show this help

Parameters:
  REPO
    Full name of the GitHub repository (user/repo)

  KEY
    The name of the secret

  VALUE
    The plain text secret value

Examples:
  secrethub save bob/vault PASSWORD p4ssw0rd
